of options. Help.

05:34.167 --> 05:37.538
Not bad. You know, he likes
preppy in an ironic way.

05:37.571 --> 05:39.673
If you lose the belt,
you should be fine.

05:39.707 --> 05:41.642
And if you let him think

05:41.675 --> 05:43.577
he came up with it,

05:43.611 --> 05:45.345
he'll love it.

05:45.379 --> 05:46.414
Untuck your shirt.

05:46.447 --> 05:48.148
No one can be skinnier
than he is.

05:48.181 --> 05:50.183
Five more pounds
is not gonna kill her.

05:50.217 --> 05:51.885
All right.
I pushed editing
to 4:30.

05:51.919 --> 05:53.320
I know how you feel
about sitting

05:53.353 --> 05:54.488
in Brad's office
after lunch.

05:54.522 --> 05:55.656
Oh, thank you.

05:55.689 --> 05:57.257
That fart candle
isn't fooling anyone.

05:57.290 --> 05:58.692
Show me, my sweet.

06:01.228 --> 06:04.965
Now, I love it. Approved.

06:08.569 --> 06:10.337
So, whatever your plans
are tomorrow night,

06:10.370 --> 06:12.773
cancel them and
come to my party.

06:12.806 --> 06:14.675
You're inviting me
to your house as a guest

06:14.708 --> 06:16.844
and not to kill a spider
or scare a coyote?

06:16.877 --> 06:18.345
Of course! I mean,
it's nothing huge.

06:18.378 --> 06:20.080
It's just, you know,
a fun little soirée

06:20.113 --> 06:21.348
with my closest friends.

06:21.381 --> 06:24.685
And you know what?
Bring your friends, too.

06:24.718 --> 06:27.054
Just as many of
them as you'd like.

06:27.087 --> 06:30.390
It's gonna be off
the chain, yo!

06:30.424 --> 06:32.560
Hook? Off the hook?

06:32.593 --> 06:34.695
BRYAN:
That's not a thing.
(laughter)

06:34.728 --> 06:36.564
Shut up.
(laughter)

06:37.665 --> 06:40.033
Okay, see you later, guys.

06:40.067 --> 06:42.870
There's not a single
person of color here.

06:42.903 --> 06:45.238
Amir is barely ethnic. He's not
even dark enough to count.

06:45.272 --> 06:47.240
I see. Would you like me to wrap
a tablecloth around his head?

06:47.274 --> 06:49.309
It's just that the blond
Imperial Wizard is coming,

06:49.342 --> 06:51.211
and everyone here is whiter
than any woman

06:51.244 --> 06:52.880
who's had Ambien sex
with Tiger Woods.

06:52.913 --> 06:56.216
Why are we letting this
small-minded woman get to us?

06:56.249 --> 06:57.918
Because we don't
want her to be right.

06:57.951 --> 06:59.219
We are not hypocrites.

06:59.252 --> 07:00.721
We are human, which means

07:00.754 --> 07:03.223
we do not always
live up to our ideals.

07:03.256 --> 07:05.258
But at least we have them.

07:05.292 --> 07:06.927
Rocky!

07:06.960 --> 07:08.562
DAVID:
Oh!

07:08.596 --> 07:09.663
Hi.
Thank God you're here.

07:09.697 --> 07:10.764
Hi.
How are you?

07:10.798 --> 07:12.933
Oh. Thank you for coming.

07:12.966 --> 07:14.001
Thank you for having me.

07:14.034 --> 07:15.469
How are you?
Well, of course.

07:15.503 --> 07:16.770
So?

07:16.804 --> 07:19.707
So?
Where are your friends?

07:24.044 --> 07:26.614
If those aren't black albinos,
we are screwed.

07:33.787 --> 07:35.088
Why the hell did you bring

07:35.122 --> 07:36.657
