to my party?

07:36.690 --> 07:38.859
Excuse me?!
David and I are
trying to convince Mrs. Forrest

07:38.892 --> 07:40.193
that we have black friends.

07:40.227 --> 07:42.362
Oh, so when you realized
you didn't, you invited me

07:42.395 --> 07:44.364
because you thought
I'd bring a bunch of sistas?

07:44.397 --> 07:47.267
Right. Only we were hoping for
more Pointer and less Bronte.

07:47.300 --> 07:49.870
