I only have black friends?

07:49.903 --> 07:51.204
That's racist.

07:51.238 --> 07:54.341
I'm horrible. I...
(sighs) I apologize.

07:54.374 --> 07:57.110
Please help me.
Lucky for you,
I invited my brother.

07:57.144 --> 07:59.212
Don't know what time he's
gonna be here, though.

07:59.246 --> 08:01.782
You know how black
people are always late.

08:01.815 --> 08:03.884
So, that's really a thing?

08:05.485 --> 08:08.021
Did you ask Amir if
he could beat-box?

08:08.055 --> 08:09.723
Excuse me.

08:09.757 --> 08:11.859
(whispers loudly):
Bryan, no!

08:11.892 --> 08:14.962
You're a waiter, so I'm going
to go out on a limb here

08:14.995 --> 08:16.363
and assume, actor, as well?

08:16.396 --> 08:18.198
Yes! And let me say,
Mr. Collins,

08:18.231 --> 08:19.232
I'm a huge fan of your show.

08:19.266 --> 08:21.234
Oh, thank you. Bryan.
Bryan. Please.

08:21.268 --> 08:23.537
Hey, how would you like
to audition for me right now?

08:23.571 --> 08:24.905
Right now?
Are you serious?

08:24.938 --> 08:26.073
Yeah, it's very simple.

08:26.106 --> 08:28.075
