you from gettin' jacked?

08:33.413 --> 08:34.815
You know, like...

08:34.848 --> 08:37.250
My boy here was gonna die if
I hadn't saved his white ass.

08:37.284 --> 08:38.986
Oh, yeah, yeah, I love that.

08:39.019 --> 08:41.088
