10:36.069 --> 10:37.938
Ooh, that looks yummy.
What is it?

10:37.971 --> 10:40.273
Meat with things on it.
Bon appétit.

10:40.307 --> 10:41.508
So how do you
know those guys?

10:41.541 --> 10:43.343
David's my doctor.

10:43.376 --> 10:44.511
He's excellent, too.

10:44.544 --> 10:46.013
