to stop talking.

10:55.055 --> 10:56.156
(laughs)

10:56.189 --> 10:57.624
Are you sure
you're single?

10:57.657 --> 11:01.729
Yeah, mm-hmm, I'm single,
all right, very, very single.

11:01.762 --> 11:02.796
(chuckling)

11:02.830 --> 11:05.899
Uh... potatoes?

11:05.933 --> 11:06.900
Yeah, let's do it.

11:06.934 --> 11:08.736
TRIPP:
Mostly I work with Father.

11:08.769 --> 11:11.571
