and my granddaughter

11:13.841 --> 11:15.876
really seem
to be hitting it off.

11:15.909 --> 11:18.211
If they start dating, I swear
to God, I'll throw myself

11:18.245 --> 11:19.512
under a bus.

11:19.546 --> 11:22.482
If they start dating, I swear
to God, there is no God.

11:22.515 --> 11:24.617
